print("All test cases pass.solution(stdin: str) -> str:
    n, k, x = map(int, stdin.split("\n")[0].split())
    a = list(map(int, stdin.split("\n")[1].split()))

    for i in range(k):
        max_index = 0
        for j in range(n):
            if a[j] * x > a[max_index] * x:
                max_index = j
        a[max_index] *= x

    return str(a[0] | a[1] | a[2] | a[3])  # If n is always 4, we can write this line more efficiently using a loop
